          <div class="data-value" id="planningToolValue" style="color:var(--green);">Yes ✓</div>
          <div class="data-note" id="planningToolNote">Florida is one of only 5 states allowing Enhanced Life Estate (Lady Bird) Deeds. This bypasses probate AND shields the home from Medicaid estate recovery. Recording cost: typically under $50.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="data-item">
          <div class="data-label">Probate Required?</div>
          <div class="data-value" id="probateStatus" style="color:var(--amber);">Likely</div>
